{"id": 225046246, "title": "Celtic - the Champions Souvenir Special is on sale now", "text": "CELTIC are Scotland\u2019s Double champions after another dramatic season of domination. Brendan Rodgers has led the Hoops to a sensational League and Scottish Cup triumph after returning as manager for a second glory-laden spell. And the Daily Record have produced a stunning new souvenir guide to celebrate Celtic\u2019s victorious season packed with unmissable features and analysis. This fantastic souvenir special is bursting with interviews, reflections and pictures from a dramatic campaign that ended in a stunning Scottish Cup final win over Rangers. Featuring articles on talismanic boss Rodgers, captain marvel Callum McGregor, golden goalie Joe Hart and midfield magician Matt O\u2019Riley the magazine is the perfect memento of a stunning season. Also included in 40 action-packed pages are six games that won the league, a full review of the cup final, man-by-man ratings and fabulous photographs from a season in Paradise. Celtic: Double Champions is the perfect way to mark a campaign to remember for Scotland\u2019s top team. You can order your copy of this special publication HERE to be delivered and it will be available to buy in participating shops from Thursday May 30, 2024.", "summary": "Celebrate Celtic's victorious season with the perfect momento", "url": "https://www.glasgowlive.co.uk/sport/football/celtic-champions-souvenir-special-sale-29258344", "image": "https://i2-prod.footballscotland.co.uk/incoming/article29258317.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200/0_Celtic.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-05-29 13:18:08", "author": "Jenny Holt", "authors": ["Jenny Holt"], "language": "en", "source_country": "gb", "sentiment": 1.0}